# Task 2: Email Template UI/UX Design

This project presents a clean and professional promotional email template designed for marketing and user engagement.

## Design Sections
- Header with brand identity
- Hero section with illustration
- Main content with clear message
- Call-to-action button
- Feature highlights
- Footer with social links and unsubscribe option

## UX Focus
- Clean and readable layout
- Clear visual hierarchy
- Responsive mobile-friendly width
- Strong call-to-action

## Tool Used
- Figma

## Designed By
- Shreya Kad
